headline: KLA Stock Rising; Key Ratings Make It One To Watch
summary: KLA products are an integral part of the chipmaking process.  Taking a look at top and bottom line numbers, the company has posted rising EPS growth in each of the last five reports.  Over the last three quarters KLA reported EPS gains of 22%, 28% and 33%, Revenue during that period grew 9%, 19% and 24% last quarter to $3.08 billion.
